OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start with
OL,6,Fsunny spells but cloud increasing
OL,7,Fthrough the morning with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain edging east, although the eastern
OL,9,FBorders remains dry and bright until
OL,10,Flate afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely cloudy through the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight with further
OL,14,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, these will
OL,15,Fbe heavy and thundery at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudier at first with heavy,
OL,18,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing.
OL,19,FThen bright or sunny spells and
OL,20,Fscattered showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
